column5: Does anyone know if this club has dissolved? I haven't been able to get on their web site for a few weeks.  I know, I know, there's only one website i should be going to...blah.blah.blah.  Cheers!
Gee I don't know Bassman. When was their last "put $10 in the kitty" meeting?
The WWW can make ya,or break ya.  To bad,there were some good apples in that bunch.
